sequenceDiagram
  title Sequence Flow: AI-Assisted Log Query Process
  participant U as Support Staff
  participant UI as Web UI
  participant AI as AI Service
  participant LLM as LLM Provider

  U->>UI: Send AI prompt
  UI->>AI: Send prompt + context
  AI->>LLM: Prompt with user visible log data
  LLM-->>AI: Return answer + summary
  AI-->>UI: Display answer + summary
  UI-->>U: Stream response